## Browser-only kin-office development settings

# Path to a Kin build directory used by ./deploy.sh in development.
# KIN_BUILD_PATH=/home/user/Projects/kin/build

# Kin Office collaboration is enabled by default on this branch.
# The browser uses /api/commands/kinoffice; Kin's generic stream proxy does not
# need private target access for Kin Office collaboration.

# Optional overrides for refreshing Euro-Office source-aligned Kin Office assets.
# EURO_OFFICE_SDKJS_REPO=https://github.com/Euro-Office/sdkjs.git
# EURO_OFFICE_SDKJS_REF=bf4a2db383f2dc9712c328e8704d3c58abb6a93e
# EURO_OFFICE_WEB_APPS_REPO=https://github.com/Euro-Office/web-apps.git
# EURO_OFFICE_WEB_APPS_REF=7cc3e23c2a881b7b3fe58e270f91b6926ec50e92
# EURO_OFFICE_CORE_REPO=https://github.com/Euro-Office/core.git
# EURO_OFFICE_CORE_REF=ab710975ac3e5b7f5ea4eea53207ec58e5c869ed
# KIN_OFFICE_PREBUILT_PACKAGES_DIR=/path/to/generated/packages
